dc_description_s: This data represents zoning for Marinette County, Wisconsin in 2021 and includes the layers 'Marinette_General_2021' and 'Marinette_Shoreland_2021.' [General: The municipal boundary feature class represents the civil/municipal boundaries in Marinette County, Wisconsin. Data is referenced to the Marinette County Coordinate System, North American Datum 1983 with the 1991 adjustment (NAD83/91).]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison.
